  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Hospitalized patients for COPD exacerbation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Hospitalization within the previous 14 days,

          -  current participation in rehabilitation program,

          -  locomotor or neurological condition or disability limiting the ability to perform
             exercise,

          -  lung transplantation or lung volume reduction surgery foreseen within 1 month after
             discharge.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
